467→
468→### Universal Probes (2)
469→
470→These probes apply to all domains.
471→
472→#### Probe 15: World Model Drift
473→
474→Measures divergence between the agent's predicted state and the actual observed state. This is the core active inference signal (Friston 2010).
475→
476→```rust
477→pub struct WorldModelDriftProbe;
