#### Probe 14: Error Rate

Monitors gate failure trend over the last N tasks.

```rust
pub struct ErrorRateProbe;

impl Probe for ErrorRateProbe {
    fn evaluate(&self, state: &EngineState) -> f32 {
        let failure_rate = state.gate_failure_rate_last_n(10);
        if failure_rate > 0.5 {
