| Cascade routing (ETH, 2024) | ~80% relative improvement over naive | 4% absolute accuracy gain | Unified routing+cascading optimal strategy |
| SATER (EMNLP 2025) | Significant (token-efficient) | Comparable | Self-aware routing, two-stage fine-tuning |

**Critical finding from GATEKEEPER (arXiv:2502.19335)**: If the confidence judge/gate reliability drops below **~80%**, cascade performance degrades rapidly. Above 80% judge reliability, cascades achieve **5x or more cost savings** with negligible quality loss.

